                      strong
                        a(href='https://www.dezshira.com/library') Asiapedia
                        | .
                    p
                      | To stay up-to-date with news and publications concerning several aspects of doing business in Asia, visit 
                      a(href='http://www.asiabriefing.com/')
                        strong Asia Briefing
